# Доменные pipeline-ы (src/lib)

## media/scanner.ts — сканирование

- `walkVideoFiles` — рекурсия, skip `.*` dirs, extensions: mkv, mp4, avi, mov, webm, …
- Skip fast path: same `filePath` + `fileSize` + `fileMtime`
- Hash: `computeFileHashPrefix` — первые 16MB (`media/file-hash.ts`)
- Move detection: same `fileHash` + `fileSize`, different path → update path in place
- Priority: `existing` at path > `movedMovie` by hash > create new DRAFT
- `parseMovieName(fileName, parentFolder)` → title, year, releaseType
- Tracks: `syncMovieTracksFromProbe` (`movies/movie-tracks.ts` + `media/apply-probe.ts`)
- Cover: `maybeExtractCover` — non-fatal

## media/ffprobe.ts — медиа-анализ

- `probeMediaFile(path, signal?)` → duration, video, audio[], subtitles[]
- Parses ffprobe JSON; HDR detection (HDR10, DV, HLG); resolution labels via `media/resolution.ts`
- Audio: `media/channels.ts` — normalizeCodec, channelsToLayout, detectAudioProfile, detectTranslationType

## media/name-parser.ts

Strips release group tags, quality, codecs from filename. Extracts year, releaseType (bluray, web-dl, …). Falls back to parent folder name for title.

## movies/movie-query.ts — фильтрация каталога

- `parseListQuery` → zod
- `buildMovieListWhere` / `buildMovieWhere` — status tabs, genre, resolution, hdr, audio scope/channels/format/translation, watched range, rating, duration, premium audio, multiRelease
- `fetchMultiReleaseMovieIds` — `release.groupBy` + `having count >= 2`
- `buildMovieOrder` — title, year, rating, watchedAt, createdAt; duration/fileSize via `fetchMovieList` release aggregates
- Audio scope: `catalog/audio-track-scope.ts` + `catalog/russian-audio-formats.ts`

## catalog/catalog-facets.ts

Counts for filter chips, scoped by active status tab. Cached on home page.

## covers/cover-storage.ts + media/mkv.ts

- Covers dir: `dataPath("covers")` → `./data/covers/`
- `saveCoverBuffer(movieId, buffer, ext)` — assert ext via `covers/cover-formats-mkv.ts`
- `extractFirstMkvAttachment` — mkvextract for embedded posters
- Franchise covers: separate naming `franchise-<id>.<ext>` in franchise cover route

## covers/cover-url.ts / covers/franchise-cover-url.ts

Build API URLs with `?v=updatedAt.getTime()` for cache busting. Never link directly to filesystem paths.

## shared/slug.ts + domain slugs

- `shared/slug.ts` — base transliteration
- `movies/movie-slug.ts` / `franchises/franchise-slug.ts` — `resolveMovieSlug`, `resolveFranchiseSlug` with numeric suffix dedup

## franchises/

- `franchise-slots.ts` — `syncFranchiseSlots` (full replace)
- `franchise-slot-placement.ts` — `placeMovieInFranchise`, `parsePlacementTarget`
- `franchise-metrics.ts` — 4K/HDR/Atmos/DTS-HD MA counts across filled slots
- `franchise-summary.ts`, `franchise-query.ts` — list queries
- `movie-franchise-memberships.ts` — attach/detach movie to slot

## merge/

- `movie-merge.ts` — `mergeMovies` / `planMerge` — manual merge transaction
- `merge-preview.ts` — merge candidate cards for `/duplicates`
- `alternative-quality.ts` — duplicate detection helpers

## catalog/archive-metrics.ts

Total/catalog/draft/excluded counts + aggregate stats for dashboard. Elite tier: `archiveEliteTierWhere` from `media/quality-predicates.ts` (specs may split across releases).

## shared/display-path.ts

Human-readable file paths (truncate home dir, storage name prefix).

## movies/load-movie-file-meta.ts

`readMovieFileMeta`, `assertMovieFileReadable` — stat + hash for manual file path entry.

## movies/build-movie-payload.ts

Assembles create/update PATCH payload from form state (tracks in `build-movie-payload-tracks.ts`).

## movies/approve-movie.ts

`approveMovie` — DRAFT → CATALOG with `movieInclude`.

## media/quality-predicates.ts

Shared audio/HDR predicates: premium Russian Atmos filter, archive elite tier, franchise slot tier inputs.

## api/client.ts

Browser-side fetch helpers (`apiFetch`, `approveMovie`, `uploadCover`) — thin wrappers over REST routes.

## db/prisma.ts

BetterSqlite3 adapter, DATABASE_URL default `file:./data/catalog.db`. Import from `@/lib/db/prisma`, types from `@/generated/prisma/client`.

## Тесты рядом

`lib/<domain>/*.test.ts` для: name-parser, movie-query, slug, ffprobe helpers, catalog-facets, channels, cover-url, franchise-slug, validators, apply-probe, build-movie-payload, archive-metrics, resolve-active-release, duration, franchise-slot-placement, approve-movie, …

При изменении логики — обновлять или добавлять тест, если поведение нетривиальное.
